{"tid":2025892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律政司向岑敖暉發信求移除污衊黨軍文章 岑敖暉強調不會移除周梓樂之死文章","createTime":"2020-05-20T14:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T14:59:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4810d88628218b3ee4f1663d5422cc7bdd72f0c","tid":2025892,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:35:22.000Z","msg":"岑敖暉收律政司信件 強調不會移除周梓樂之死文章<br />\n20.05.2020 22:10<br />\n<br />\n荃灣區議員岑敖暉收到律政司信件，要求移除有關科大學生周梓樂之死的文章。涉及的是岑敖暉月初一篇「周梓樂被香港警察謀殺身亡，半年」的文章，岑敖暉在社交網站指，律政司在信中指他鼓吹煽動暴力，或違反法庭禁制令，要求在7日內移除文章。岑敖暉指，曾想過刪除文章，但認為政權希望以言入罪，決定不遵從。<br />\n<br />\n警方上星期已經發信予岑敖暉，指他信口開河抹黑警隊，要求停止散播謠言，並不排除有進一步法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288898&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288898%26csid%3D261_341&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=38607378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288898&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b3d1a0e448341c08ea075ed352ed3d57433c55e0","tid":2025892,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"謠言？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X8nraLlxbGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX8nraLlxbGM&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=abcd56f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X8nraLlxbGM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRZNu1T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRZNu1T.png&h=784ff463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/92GfPoRaqMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F92GfPoRaqMA&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=5c721d97\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/92GfPoRaqMA</a>"},{"pid":"e320b9e57c44fc4616143f8a6d3